(11, 'voice', '最初のボイス', '"Making Edo Kiriko was so much fun! I met a lot of new people and experienced a lot of new things. The glass carving was harder than I thought, but I am very happy with my glass. I would definitely love to participate in another SAMURAI MEETUPS event." - Catherine Anderberg', '"Making Edo Kiriko was so much fun! I met a lot of new people and experienced a lot of new things. The glass carving was harder than I thought, but I am very happy with my glass. I would definitely love to participate in another SAMURAI MEETUPS event." - Catherine Anderberg', NULL),
(12, 'voice', '最後のボイス', '"The tour was great. Everyone is really friendly and helpful. It was fun doing something creative in a really relaxed environment. Everyone speaks good English which made conversation and instructions really easy." - Ben Hughes', '"The tour was great. Everyone is really friendly and helpful. It was fun doing something creative in a really relaxed environment. Everyone speaks good English which made conversation and instructions really easy." - Ben Hughes', NULL),
